SLMP_END_CODE_MESSAGE(0x3008, "・In the redundant system with redundant extension base unit, a module name other than \"RJ71EN71(E+E)\" and \"RJ71EN71(Q)\" is set on the extension base.・\"RJ71GP21-SX\" or \"RJ71GP21S-SX\" is selected for the module name in a redundant system.・\"RJ71GP21-SX (R)\" or \"RJ71GP21S-SX (R)\" is selected for the module name in a system other than a redundant system.・\"RJ71GF11-T2\" is selected for the module name in a redundant system.・\"RJ71GF11-T2 (MR)\", \"RJ71GF11-T2 (SR)\", or \"RJ71GF11-T2 (LR)\" is selected for the module name in a system other than a redundant system.")
SLMP_END_CODE_MESSAGE(0x3019, "・When mounting a module on the main base unit in the redundant system, \"Not Use\" is set to \"To Use or Not to Use Redundant System Settings\" under \"Application Settings\".・When mounting a module on the extension base unit in the redundant system with redundant extension base unit, \"Use\" is set to \"To Use or Not to Use Redundant System Settings\" under \"Application Settings\".")
